'Lie like a dog, ',,,

18:32.666 --> 18:34.998
''often enough that it is almost a clichÃ©,

18:35.335 --> 18:37.030
''But more often than not,,,

18:37.137 --> 18:39.799
''if someone is lying to you,
they are a person,

18:39.973 --> 18:43.101
''We all know a certain person
who is lying to her husband,

18:43.209 --> 18:46.804
''Every time we look the other way,
we add a lie to a lie,

